channel.title: [RELEASE] Nuthesian god stuff [RELEASE]
channel.description:
Well...I've decided to release my Nuthesian god stuff. If you havent heard of it or seen it yet, here is the original thread:
[URL=http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,320137.0.html]http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,320137.0.html[/URL]
Download the models here and read the readme:
[URL=http://www.mediafire.com/file/mmogyquu2le/Release.zip]http://www.mediafire.com/file/mmogyquu2le/Release.zip[/URL]
Thanks guys for all the feedback!!!
P.S. Feel free to make Nuthesian god related stuff if you want. Please post any new armor, weapons, npc, or anything you make here and ill give you my feedback!!!
[size=10pt]Also, i would like some posts and not just all downloads I wont be a stickler for it but please post when you download![/size]
